chs: 你按时送好了快递！获得2个随机动作！
eng: You finished the delivery on time! Gain 2 actions!
You Win! Thank for playing! LD53

chs: 在规定的时间内拾取地上的快递，并加速抵达目的地
eng: Finish the delivery on time. Pick up the box on the road.

chs: 撞车会丢失所有快递，需要足够多的快递才算完成
eng: You will lose all boxes when crashing. Finish the level with enough boxes.

chs: QWER来控制车辆，并不断构建你的控制链条
eng: QWER to control the car. Build your control chain by new actions.

chs: 关卡结束后可以获得新的动作，点击动作来更换到对应键位
eng: Gain new actions after the level. Click it to change into action chain.
